QUICK REFERENCE — Common Commands

SURVEYING YOUR COUNTRY
  census *              sector status (pop, eff, mob, food)
  resource *            mineral deposits
  commodity *           all goods in each sector
  map *                 graphical map
  nation                treasury, tech, reserve
  power                 nation power rankings
  ship *                list your ships
  update                time until next update

GROWING YOUR TERRITORY
  explore X,Y path c N  send N civs along path to claim sectors
    path chars: u=upper-right  j=right  n=lower-right
                b=lower-left   g=left   y=upper-left

SECTORS
  des X,Y type          redesignate sector (see info sector-types)
  census * ?des=a       census only agribusiness sectors

COMMODITIES
  move food 0,0 100 4,-2    move 100 food from capital to 4,-2
  threshold food 0,0 2000   keep 2000 food in capital
  deliver food X,Y 200 $    deliver surplus to dist center
  distribute * 0,0          all sectors use capital as dist hub

SHIPS
  build s 6,0 0 1       build fishing boat (type 0) at harbor 6,0
  ship *                list ships
  navigate 0 jjjj       move ship 0 four sectors right
  load food 0 500       load 500 food onto ship 0
  unload food 0 200     unload 200 food from ship 0

MILITARY
  enlist 0,0 100        deploy 100 reserve troops to capital
  demobilize * -10      put excess mil in reserve (keep 10/sector)
  attack X,Y 0,0        attack X,Y from capital

DIPLOMACY
  relations             see stances with all countries
  declare N war         declare war on country N
  telegram N message    send private message
  announce message      public broadcast to all

INFORMATION
  info topic            help on any topic
  show s b              ship build requirements
  show l b              land unit requirements
  version               server settings
  syntax                how sector/ship specs work

SEE ALSO
  info  overview  basics  syntax  sector-types
